WEBVTT

00:04:58.280 --> 00:05:00.656
on the real and everyday lives
of ordinary people

00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:03.560
with a series of delicious little details.

00:05:05.440 --> 00:05:09.120
In the countryside,
the hills are landscaped and farmed.

00:05:11.280 --> 00:05:14.976
Crops are being sown,
hoed, reaped, milled, plowed,

00:05:15.000 --> 00:05:16.400
all in one picture.

00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:21.720
Crops and livestock
are being brought to market.

00:05:23.480 --> 00:05:25.800
In the city, builders raise a tower.

00:05:28.400 --> 00:05:32.216
People attend a law lecture,
a TED Talk of the 14th century.